􏷘+􏷗􏷒pack 8 bool params into a byte􏷑
􏷐Packs eight BOOLs into a single BYTE of a buffer􏷏
􏶠uses bit shifts on each index of the bool array
note: the bits will be in reverse order of the bools passed in
example: {􏵱,􏵱,􏵱,􏵱,􏵱,􏵱,􏵱,􏵰}
becomes: 01111111􏶡
